好，我不介意……","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"ev123-ep1-036","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"透子","body":"等一下！　為什麼要往後退！\n紗夜學姊也要入鏡喔！　好的，請拿著這個然後笑一個！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"surprised01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"ev123-ep1-037","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"紗夜","body":"這、這個不行！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":22,"motionName":"shame01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":22,"voiceId":"ev123-ep1-038","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":27}],"windowDisplayName":"透子","body":"欸～，不行嗎……\n話說沒想到紗夜學姊竟然會選這種的耶","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":27,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":27,"voiceId":"ev123-ep1-039","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":22}],"windowDisplayName":"紗夜","body":"我、我也沒想到外觀居然是這樣子！\n菜單上只有寫「特調巧克力拿鐵」，\n要是有放照片，我絕對不會點這個！","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFact